        <div class="mb-16 flex items-center justify-center flex-wrap gap-6">
          <span class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold">Multi Columns.</span>
          <span class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold">Multi Accounts.</span>
          <span class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold">Note Discovery.</span>
          <span class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold">Negentropy.</span>
          <span class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-black italic">
            And a lot of things.
          </span>
